{"operationName":"getFlexiblePortfolios","variables":{},"query":"query getFlexiblePortfolios {
  flexiblePortfolios(orderBy: startDate, orderDirection: desc) {
    ...BerylliumFlexiblePortfolioFields
    __typename
  }
}

fragment BerylliumFlexiblePortfolioFields on FlexiblePortfolio {
  id
  chainId
  name
  symbol
  status
  factoryAddress
  asset {
    id
    chainId
    name
    symbol
    decimals
    __typename
  }
  loans {
    id
    loanId
    instrumentAddress
    recipient
    principal
    instrumentType
    ... on FixedInterestOnlyLoan {
      periodPayment
      status
      periodCount
      periodDuration
      currentPeriodEndDate
      periodsRepaid
      gracePeriod
      canBeRepaidAfterDefault
      endDate
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
  startDate
  endDate
  maxSize
  manager {
    id
    chainId
    __typename
  }
  withdrawController
  depositController {
    id
    lenderVerifier
    __typename
  }
  transferController
  totalAssets
  virtualTokenBalance
  protocolFeeRate
  managerFeeRate
  __typename
}
"}

{"operationName":"getFlexiblePortfolios","variables":{},"query":"query getFlexiblePortfolios {
  flexiblePortfolios(orderBy: startDate, orderDirection: desc) {
    ...BerylliumFlexiblePortfolioFields
    __typename
  }
}

fragment BerylliumFlexiblePortfolioFields on FlexiblePortfolio {
  id
  chainId
  name
  symbol
  status
  factoryAddress
  asset {
    id
    chainId
    name
    symbol
    decimals
    __typename
  }
  loans {
    id
    loanId
    instrumentAddress
    recipient
    principal
    instrumentType
    ... on FixedInterestOnlyLoan {
      periodPayment
      status
      periodCount
      periodDuration
      currentPeriodEndDate
      periodsRepaid
      gracePeriod
      canBeRepaidAfterDefault
      endDate
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
  startDate
  endDate
  maxSize
  manager {
    id
    chainId
    __typename
  }
  withdrawController
  depositController {
    id
    lenderVerifier
    __typename
  }
  transferController
  totalAssets
  virtualTokenBalance
  protocolFeeRate
  managerFeeRate
  __typename
}
"}
